<p><strong>Ingredients</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>1 or 2 lemon wedges</li>
  <li>1 teaspoon turmeric</li>
  <li>Honey (as much as your heart desires!)</li>
  <li>6 - 8 oz. water</li>
  <li>Your favorite mug :)</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Recipe</strong></p>

<ol>
  <li>Heat 6 - 8 oz. of water until steaming!</li>
  <li>Pour water into your fav mug &lt;3</li>
  <li>Add 1 teaspoon of turmeric</li>
  <li>Squeeze 1 or 2 wedges of lemon into water</li>
  <li>Add honey and sweeten to taste</li>
  <li>Stir and enjoy!</li>
</ol>

<p>Caution: Let cool 5 - 10 min. before your first sip!</p>

<p>We hope you’re safe &amp; in good health! Bring some warmth to your shelter-in-place with this yummy turmeric tea. Perfect for relieving a dry, itchy throat—or enjoying with your favorite book! Comfort is only a sip away :)</p>
